The Dispatch Registrar has received an open commission from the Covenant Council for an expedition-grade survey of the Sunken Sanctum. The structure has no current documentation in any known reference archive, and the commission has been open since the last expedition crew filed an incomplete record. Chart every accessible chamber and corridor within the Sanctum and return with a full navigation record.
Your Sunken Sanctum survey has been filed with the Covenant Council's expedition archive. The Dispatch Registrar has marked the long-standing commission fulfilled and noted that this is the first complete survey of the Sanctum's full accessible extent.
